gmd:title.gco:CharacterString: SeaDataCloud Black Sea Temperature and Salinity Climatology V2

gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: The SDC_BLS_CLIM_TS_V2 product contains Temperature and Salinity Climatologies for Black Sea including the seasonal and monthly fields for period 1955-2019 and seasonal fields for 6 decades starting from 1955 to 2019.  The climatic fields were computed from the integrated Black Sea dataset that combines data extracted from the 3 major sources: 1) SeaDataNet infrastructure, 2) World Ocean Database, and 3) Coriolis Ocean Dataset for Reanalysis. The computation was done with the DIVAnd (Data-Interpolating Variational Analysis in n dimensions), version 2.6.4.

gmd:statement.gco:CharacterString:

The Quality Control was performed as described in: Myroshnychenko Volodymyr (2020). SeaDataCloud Temperature and Salinity Historical Data Collection for the Black Sea (Version 2). Product Information Document (PIDoc). https://doi.org/10.13155/77211
